OLX Car Cover Scraper
A Python script that scrapes car cover listings from OLX India and saves them to a CSV file.
Features

Searches for "car cover" products on OLX India (www.olx.in/items/q-car-cover)
Extracts key information: title, price, location, date posted, and URL
Saves results to a CSV file in the olx_results directory
Handles errors gracefully and includes random delays to avoid rate limiting

Requirements

Python 3.6 or higher
Required packages:

requests
beautifulsoup4
csv (standard library)
datetime (standard library)
time (standard library)
random (standard library)
os (standard library)



Installation

Clone this repository:

git clone https://github.com/yourusername/olx-car-cover-scraper.git
cd olx-car-cover-scraper

Install the required packages:

pip install -r requirements.txt
Usage
Run the script with Python:
python olx_scraper.py
The script will:

Create an olx_results directory if it doesn't exist
Scrape up to 3 pages of car cover listings from OLX India
Save the results to a timestamped CSV file in the olx_results directory

Disclaimer
This scraper is for educational purposes only. Using web scrapers may be against the terms of service of some websites. Please use responsibly and respect the website's robots.txt file and rate limits.
